				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6014661/scp-3359#post-3816072</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 28 May 2018 18:23:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DrDromeus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3785128</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The idea, which I may have not done too well, was that the part about being transformed by eating the offerings was only discovered and added to the file after addendum -04, which states that the replacement process works. For all rights and purposes, this was just a test to understand what the deal is with those bowls of food that replace themselves.</p> 
				 	]]>
